<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒并不知道这个观音菩萨是红孩儿变的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧有麻烦了。”八戒对着假观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有个叫红孩儿的妖怪要吃了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您能帮帮我们吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。”假观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道红孩儿。他人很好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不相信他会伤害唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们去红孩儿的洞穴找他谈谈吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和假观音菩萨飞到了红孩儿的洞穴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒先走了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿变回了自己，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后悄悄地走到了八戒身后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用一个大麻袋套住了八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，怎么回事儿？”八戒大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是观音菩萨，傻瓜！”红孩儿大笑道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是红孩儿！现在你跑不掉了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿把八戒关进了一间屋子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒为什么还不回来？”悟净问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空皱着眉头说：“他可能又去打瞌睡了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那头猪很懒。”悟净点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，他确实很懒。我们现在要怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得去一下红孩儿的洞穴。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去看一下唐僧是否还活着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后我去找观音菩萨。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变成了一只蜜蜂，向山上飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从洞门进去，经过一条很长的隧道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快他就听到了唐僧哭的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父害怕了。”悟空想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“至少他还活着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，悟空听到了一声尖叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是八戒。“妖怪！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你怎么敢变成观音菩萨的样子来骗我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哈！”悟空想，“原来八戒没有打瞌睡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我得立刻去找真的观音菩萨。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空飞出了洞穴，告诉悟净他看到的情况，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他跳到空中向南飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在观音亭找到了观音菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，你怎么来了？”观音菩萨问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有麻烦了，观音菩萨。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧被一个叫红孩儿的妖怪抓了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那妖怪有三昧真火，我们没法扑灭它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒本来要来向你求助，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但那妖怪变成了你的样子，骗了八戒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨气得脸通红。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那妖怪居然敢变成我的样子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨拿起净瓶，生气地走出了观音亭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把净瓶扔进了海里。净瓶沉了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大吃一惊。“那净瓶是佛祖的宝贝啊！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你为什么要扔了它？”观音菩萨没有回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，海水开始翻滚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>净瓶又出现了。它在一只巨大的海龟背上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海龟爬到了岸上，低头行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，下去把净瓶拿回来吧。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跑下山，想拿起净瓶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”悟空用尽了自己所有力气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不管他用多大力气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他都没办法把净瓶拿起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“观音菩萨！”他大叫，“我不明白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这只是个小小的净瓶，我居然拿不起来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨走下了山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“净瓶经过了世界的河流和海洋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在那里面装着一个海洋的水——甘露。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那水可以灭了红孩儿的火。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨用一只手拿起了净瓶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她举起另一只手，空中出现了很多把宝剑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她挥舞宝剑，它们变成了一个巨大的莲花台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在需要的东西都准备完了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨说，“我们走吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>